                        <interp inst="t18480918-2153-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aped 23.—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18480918-2153-punishment-78" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18480918-2153-punishment-78" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2153-18480918 t18480918-2153-punishment-78"></join>Transported for Seven Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">The prosecutor stated he had been robbed three times within three week, and that the prisoner was in the habit of coming to his house all that lime.</hi>)</p>
